commentText:

Default is none: When no explicit output Record gets passed into an_{@code execute} method, CCI's {@code Interaction.execute} variant_that returns an output Record will be called._

codeText: protected RecordFactory getRecordFactory(ConnectionFactory connectionFactory) throws ResourceException {_		try {_			return connectionFactory.getRecordFactory()__		}_		catch (NotSupportedException ex) {_			return new NotSupportedRecordFactory()__		}_	}
